name: 甘奈
text: 最近は頑張ってたつもりなんだけどなー……
trans: And I was so sure I'd been doing well lately...

name: プロデューサー
text:
また次頑張ろう！
甘奈なら、絶対できる！
trans:
Let's give it another shot next time!
I know you can do it, Amana!

name: 甘奈
text:
事務所に戻ったら今日の反省点をはっきりさせたいから
映像見せてね！
trans:
When we get back to the office, please show me
today's footage so I can figure out what I need to
work on.

name: プロデューサー
text: ああ、しっかりと今回の反省を次に生かしていこう！
trans:
Sure thing. Let's use this as a lesson to prepare for
the next one.

name: 甘奈
text: ありがと！　次は絶対に合格してみせるんだから！
trans:
Thanks! Next time I'm totally gonna pass, just
wait and see!
